		<title>客单价从8元暴涨至35元，销量却暴跌70%：年轻人为何抛弃‘炸串刺客’？</title>
		<link>https://www.tmtpost.com/7637677.html</link>
		<comments>https://www.tmtpost.com/7637677.html#comments</comments>
				<pubDate>Fri, 25 Jul 2025 15:32:51 +0800</pubDate>
						<dc:creator>听风译码</dc:creator>

